{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"15101","heading":"Officers in designated competitive categories","label":"15101 Officers in designated competitive categories","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s15101","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/stE/ptIII/ch1413","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs15101","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—Authority to Designate Competitive Categories of Officers","label":"a .—Authority to Designate Competitive Categories of Officers","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s15101/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s15101","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs15101%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Each Secretary of a military department may designate one or more competitive categories for promotion of officers under that are under the jurisdiction of such Secretary as a competitive category of officers whose promotion, retirement, and continuation on the reserve active-status list shall be subject to the provisions of this chapter.section 14005 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Limitation on Exercise of Authority","label":"b .—Limitation on Exercise of Authority","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s15101/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s15101","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs15101%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s15101/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s15101/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs15101%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A detailed description of officer requirements for officers within the competitive category.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s15101/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s15101/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs15101%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"An explanation of the number of opportunities for consideration for promotion to each particular grade, and an estimate of promotion timing, within the competitive category.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s15101/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s15101/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs15101%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"An estimate of the size of the promotion zone for each grade within the competitive category.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s15101/b/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s15101/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs15101%2Fb%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A description of any other matters the Secretary considered in determining to designate the competitive category for purposes of this chapter.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
